- 'data points' refer to unique pieces of data that can be shared;
- 'most frequently shared' means the data point with the highest number of share events.

- 'pending' status indicates that the data points have not yet been fully shared with the user;
- '2-meter temperature (t2m)' is the temperature measured at 2 meters above the ground;
- 'Alice Johnson' is the user with whom the data points are being shared.

sql:
